TO DEPLOY:
- clone submodules (library | public/rialtoPublicLibrary)
	Run these commands from your project root directory:
		rm -r public/rialtoPublicLibrary
		git submodule add https://github.com/NovumWare/Rialto_Public_Library.git public/rialtoPublicLibrary
		rm -r library/NovumWarePublicLibrary
		git submodule add https://github.com/NovumWare/NovumWarePublicLibrary.git library/NovumWarePublicLibrary
- update MySQL stuff in application/configs/local_settings.ini
- create log file with write permission at logs/log.txt
- create smarty temp folder with write permission at tmp/templates_c
- copy file and update @siteRoot in public/stylesheets/less/local_variables.less
- define $_sessionNamespace in the bootstrap